text: (dani phalitanga!) Allah kapata visvasulayina purusulanu mariyu kapata visvasulayina strilanu mariyu allah ku sati kalpince purusulanu mariyu sati kalpince strilanu siksistadu; mariyu visvasulaina purusula mariyu visvasulaina strila pascattapanni angikaristadu. Mariyu allah ksamasiludu, apara karuna pradata
